English (en): Citizen OS - an e-decisionmaking platform for communities.
Citizen OS enables participative discussion and voting for groups, when getting together offline or online at the same time is not an option.
e-decisionmaking, e-governance, e-democracy, democracy, direct democracy, liquid democracy
